Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:16.88,yinglv,NTP,0,0,0,,あなたはあたしだけの人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:19.10,yinglv,NTP,0,0,0,,俺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:21.84,yinglv,NTP,0,0,0,,チィは秀樹が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:24.96,yinglv,NTP,0,0,0,,秀樹はチィが好き
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:27.42,yinglv,NTP,0,0,0,,俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.76,0:21:37.48,yinglv,NTP,0,0,0,,これが
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:44.32,yinglv,NTP,0,0,0,,本当にお店休んでも良かったんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:45.96,yinglv,NTP,0,0,0,,おい
